5-07T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"740dd985b5d41a95e2d21e4ab79cb9c307e8268f","tid":1142224,"uid":35063,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"同高雄發大財條撚樣一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9b86441075bb9d5888ce774c4eaac3d6f660c9","tid":1142224,"uid":36178,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"關門就即係關門, 無關嘅門即係無關"},{"pid":"d5cb997a56561ba6bc18c93433377636d172bcf6","tid":1142224,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"反正中国又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed96add3ae123c4accb7a777467775c91755c610","tid":1142224,"uid":121580,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"740dd985b5d41a95e2d21e4ab79cb9c307e8268f","tid":1142224,"uid":35063,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"同高雄發大財條撚樣一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:13:35.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財xN"},{"pid":"aef70d4d2e821a155a22de68e49fb5acd7e81e06","tid":1142224,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"中國發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04dd571a233e9b52d3936f3edf35bb416c02e22","tid":1142224,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:15:08.000Z","msg":"2019年5月6日外交部发言人耿爽主持例行记者会<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/jzhsl_673025/t1661103.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Ffyrbt_673021%2Fjzhsl_673025%2Ft1661103.shtml&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=9fca3d78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/jzhsl_673025/t1661103.shtml</a><br />\n问：第一个问题，你提到中方团队正在准备赴美磋商，是本周去吗？第二个问题，中方团队抵美时，可能正赶上美国对中国产品加征关税。中方是否认为这为中美经贸磋商取得进展创造了有利环境？<br />\n<br />\n  答：关于你关心的磋商的具体情况和安排，建议你向主管部门询问。<br />\n<br />\n  关于美方威胁对中国部分产品加征关税，我刚才说过了，类似这样的情况以前多次出现过。中方的立场态度一直很明确，美方也非常清楚。<br />\n<br />\n  问：我想再问一下有关中美经贸磋商的问题，你提到中方团队正在准备赴美磋商，是为了确保磋商还会按计划于周三开始吗？<br />\n<br />\n  答：我能告诉你的是，我们希望美方与中方共同努力，相向而行，争取在相互尊重基础上达成一个互利双赢的协议。<br />\n<br />\n  具体问题恐怕你只能去问主管部门。<br />\n<br />\n  问：你提到让我们去问有关部门，我们向他们发传真询问中美贸易磋商是否会如期进行，但没有收到回复。请问我们到底该问哪个有关部门？<br />\n<br />\n   答：有关部门当然就是有关的部门了。无关的就不能称为有关部门。所以我建议你还是要向他们询问。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406e331845bf203e835fae03fb30898f2f2618ca","tid":1142224,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"有關部門當然就是有關的部門了。無關的就不能稱為有關部門。所以我建議你還是要向他們詢問。"},{"pid":"ee1dfa80c73a8784bd9d8653d2c9383a5dfa8fa7","tid":1142224,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"問佢要查詢邊個部門<br />\n佢就解釋你聽咩係有關部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82b58a8e8a94aa589b734a8a0f9291ad699e43f","tid":1142224,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"使乜講咁多，直接答中國人民無權知道咪贏晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acf10d6d0a77ff039bad774401f836b488e4cb8","tid":1142224,"uid":7439,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nanrenwo.net/uploads/allimg/150723/8122-150H3154557.j